  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Midnight Evil</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's late at night and you've discovered a mysterious book that seems to have its own evil agenda. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you begin to read through it, you realize that you are not alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only way to free yourself from this fiendish nightmare is to finish reading. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this story driven, voice activated, sit-and-survive horror game, don't forget to check your surroundings..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, be sure to make direct eye contact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you survive the night?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between <strong>Narrate Mode</strong> (speak into microphone) or <strong>Listen Mode</strong> (fully voice acted - all other Windows OS's) to make it through the chapters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A familiar Sit-And-Survive play style!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A full spooky narrative about ancient beings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to play with your microphone!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice acted if you don't have a microphone! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual Operating System / Game Console, Otori; with unlockable games and applications!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming cheesy 80's horror environment and comedic relief!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nick Gloom's self-absorbed ego.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.poster.avif?t=1772917357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.webm?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.mp4?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.poster.avif?t=1772917357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.webm?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.mp4?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mic Not Working?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure Time & Language -> Speech -> Speech Language = English (United States)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Microphone Access is enabled via Windows Microphone Privacy Settings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allow Apps to Access Your Microphone via Windows Microphone Privacy Settings.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Midnight Evil</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's late at night and you've discovered a mysterious book that seems to have its own evil agenda. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you begin to read through it, you realize that you are not alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only way to free yourself from this fiendish nightmare is to finish reading. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this story driven, voice activated, sit-and-survive horror game, don't forget to check your surroundings..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, be sure to make direct eye contact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you survive the night?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between <strong>Narrate Mode</strong> (speak into microphone) or <strong>Listen Mode</strong> (fully voice acted - all other Windows OS's) to make it through the chapters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A familiar Sit-And-Survive play style!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A full spooky narrative about ancient beings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ability to play with your microphone!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voice acted if you don't have a microphone! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Virtual Operating System / Game Console, Otori; with unlockable games and applications!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming cheesy 80's horror environment and comedic relief!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nick Gloom's self-absorbed ego.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.poster.avif?t=1772917357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.webm?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/e0ff93489d70cb94f9359f9f0c9ac48b.mp4?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.poster.avif?t=1772917357\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.webm?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1030360/extras/fdf17ed4ae041f145ecfe58d70e2d7fb.mp4?t=1772917357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mic Not Working?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ensure Time & Language -> Speech -> Speech Language = English (United States)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Microphone Access is enabled via Windows Microphone Privacy Settings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allow Apps to Access Your Microphone via Windows Microphone Privacy Settings.</p></li></ul>",
